</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Kein Sidecar notwendig</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Builder Images +30MB gr=C3=B6sser</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Explizite Aktivierung im Repo (via estaTektonPip=
eline.json)</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Shutdown des Kubedock Servers muss sichergestell=
t werden</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div></td>
</tr>
